section:

  Client server API



  The client server API of &product_name; allows you to send and
  retrieve data to and from a MariaDB database server. It supports also
  communication with databases from other vendors, like Percona or Oracle.



  Several other client APIs, like MariaDB Connector/ODBC use &product_name;
  to communicate with a MariaDB database server.


